{"tid":1544880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人之殤] 永遠懷念831死亡香港人 - 聽日係頭七","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T00:56:09.000Z","uid":92347,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a006c9cd4ed268c126a6a32e17e6d41ab4a34a7b","tid":1544880,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[大整合] 831事件未必得2個死<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[大整合] 831事件未必得2個死(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544727</a><br />\n<br />\n[簡易懶人包] 真相浮現，831太子站極可能真係有人死，已非坊間流言既程度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542384</a><br />\n<br />\n以上有齊fc既資料，有人證，有失蹤人口，有可疑既地方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>聽日831，你地直接死於港共政權手下<br />\n對唔住，呢一刻未清楚你地咩名生前發生咩事，但我地會盡一切努力幫你還清真相<br />\n我地會盡一生時間，去為你地平反<br />\n我地絕不原諒令你地直接死亡既黑警/中共</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n你地一路好走！希望你地係另一邊睇到光復後既香港，睇到煲底除底口罩既香港人!<br />\n我地唔會忘記你，2019年8月31日晚，係我地呢代香港人之殤<br />\n永遠懷念</span></strong>"},{"pid":"aed495fd4cfefb5569d14b6aa45b85277324ce94","tid":1544880,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7402e4ccd931f80aa1c2e75b3b2865c6933002fd","tid":1544880,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4634f1e0b0b4c03fecae37e01356fcbc7926bca0","tid":1544880,"uid":92347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">號召各位巴打<br />\n聽日9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a880e4f82f2c9e7f889972d2009973e024e62462","tid":1544880,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"size=5]<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ 極緊急！！ ]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一人一信<br />\n<br />\n向國會議員表達通過<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》既意願！！！！</span></span>[/size=5]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543156</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">上面個post有template!!!!!</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以下係目標人物(入網站遞交意見書！) ：</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-la